MEDICAL DOCTOR: Advanced trauma care and surgery

Category: Medical
Base skill: 55% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Palladium's top-tier medical skill: surgery, advanced trauma care,
diagnosis, and treatment beyond what First Aid or Paramedic training
covers. Body Fixers, Cyber-Docs, and other dedicated medical OCCs
build their whole profession around it.

Commands: limbs <target> / replace <target> <limb>
  Knowing any level of Medical Doctor is enough to use both commands;
  neither rolls your percentage. "limbs" senses a target's overall
  condition and any narratively severed limbs. "replace" regenerates
  one severed limb. Limb severing in AetherMUD is narrative only: it
  never changes stats or damage, so replace restores appearance and
  story state, not a combat effect.

